### Advanced CSS Effects

Combine CSS properties for stunning visual effects.

---

### Glassmorphism

```css
.glass {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  border-radius: 16px;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}
```

---

### Neumorphism

```css
.neumorphic {
  background: #e0e5ec;
  border-radius: 20px;
  box-shadow:
    20px 20px 60px #bec3c9,
    -20px -20px 60px #ffffff;
}

.neumorphic-inset {
  background: #e0e5ec;
  border-radius: 20px;
  box-shadow:
    inset 8px 8px 16px #bec3c9,
    inset -8px -8px 16px #ffffff;
}
```

---

### Gradient Border

```css
.gradient-border {
  border: 4px solid transparent;
  border-image: linear-gradient(45deg, #f06, #3cf) 1;
}

/* Alternative with pseudo-element */
.gradient-border-2 {
  position: relative;
  background: white;
  border-radius: 10px;
}

.gradient-border-2::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  inset: -3px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  background: linear-gradient(45deg, #f06, #3cf);
  z-index: -1;
}
```

---

### Text Gradient

```css
.gradient-text {
  background: linear-gradient(45deg, #f06, #3cf);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  background-clip: text;
  color: transparent;
}
```

---

### Clip Path Shapes

```css
.clip-diamond {
  clip-path: polygon(50% 0%, 100% 50%, 50% 100%, 0% 50%);
}

.clip-hexagon {
  clip-path: polygon(25% 0%, 75% 0%, 100% 50%, 75% 100%, 25% 100%, 0% 50%);
}

.clip-star {
  clip-path: polygon(50% 0%, 61% 35%, 98% 35%, 68% 57%, 79% 91%, 50% 70%, 21% 91%, 32% 57%, 2% 35%, 39% 35%);
}
```

---

### Blend Modes

```css
.blend-multiply { mix-blend-mode: multiply; }
.blend-screen { mix-blend-mode: screen; }
.blend-overlay { mix-blend-mode: overlay; }
.blend-difference { mix-blend-mode: difference; }

/* Background blend */
.bg-blend {
  background-image: url('img.jpg'), linear-gradient(red, blue);
  background-blend-mode: overlay;
}
```

---

### Smooth Scrolling

```css
html {
  scroll-behavior: smooth;
}
```

---

> **Best Practice:** Use `backdrop-filter` sparingly as it can impact performance. Prefer `clip-path` for creative shapes.
